 \"to\": 2004}, {\"ngram\": \"the 1920 Summer Games\", \"from\": 2016, \"to\": 2037}, {\"ngram\": \"the build-up\", \"from\": 2059, \"to\": 2071}, {\"ngram\": \"the 1936 Olympics\", \"from\": 2075, \"to\": 2092}, {\"ngram\": \"a global icon\", \"from\": 2140, \"to\": 2153}]}, {\"sentence\": \"And over time, the meaning of the colours has changed.\", \"from\": 2155, \"to\": 2209, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"time\", \"from\": 2164, \"to\": 2168}, {\"ngram\": \"the meaning\", \"from\": 2170, \"to\": 2181}, {\"ngram\": \"the colours\", \"from\": 2185, \"to\": 2196}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Fast forward to today and many believe each inhabited continent is represented with a ring and a designated colour.\", \"from\": 2210, \"to\": 2325, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"today\", \"from\": 2226, \"to\": 2231}, {\"ngram\": \"each inhabited continent\", \"from\": 2249, \"to\": 2273}, {\"ngram\": \"a ring\", \"from\": 2294, \"to\": 2300}, {\"ngram\": \"a designated colour\", \"from\": 2305, \"to\": 2324}]}, {\"sentence\": \"We use your sign-up to provide content in ways you have consented to and to improve our understanding of you.\", \"from\": 2327, \"to\": 2436, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"your sign-up\", \"from\": 2334, \"to\": 2346}, {\"ngram\": \"content\", \"from\": 2358, \"to\": 2365}, {\"ngram\": \"ways\", \"from\": 2369, \"to\": 2373}, {\"ngram\": \"our understanding\", \"from\": 2411, \"to\": 2428}]}, {\"sentence\": \"This may include adverts from us and 3rd parties based on our understanding.\", \"from\": 2437, \"to\": 2513, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"adverts\", \"from\": 2454, \"to\": 2461}, {\"ngram\": \"us\", \"from\": 2467, \"to\": 2469}, {\"ngram\": \"3rd parties\", \"from\": 2474, \"to\": 2485}, {\"ngram\": \"our understanding\", \"from\": 2495, \"to\": 2512}]}, {\"sentence\": \"You can unsubscribe at any time.\", \"from\": 2514, \"to\": 2546, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"any time\", \"from\": 2537, \"to\": 2545}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Read ourPrivacy Policy However, that too is a myth, and the Olympic Charter dictates that no colour is attributed to any specific continent.\", \"from\": 2547, \"to\": 2688, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"ourPrivacy Policy\", \"from\": 2552, \"to\": 2569}, {\"ngram\": \"a myth\", \"from\": 2591, \"to\": 2597}, {\"ngram\": \"the Olympic Charter\", \"from\": 2603, \"to\": 2622}, {\"ngram\": \"no colour\", \"from\": 2637, \"to\": 2646}, {\"ngram\": \"any specific continent\", \"from\": 2664, \"to\": 2686}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Nonetheless, many still prefer to believe in their nation (or continent) being represented by one colour in particular.\", \"from\": 2689, \"to\": 2808, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"their nation\", \"from\": 2734, \"to\": 2746}, {\"ngram\": \"continent\", \"from\": 2751, \"to\": 2760}, {\"ngram\": \"one colour\", \"from\": 2783, \"to\": 2793}]}, {\"sentence\": \"So, the often forgotten modern meaning behind the five colours of the Olympic rings is that there is not one.\", \"from\": 2810, \"to\": 2919, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the often forgotten modern meaning\", \"from\": 2814, \"to\": 2848}, {\"ngram\": \"the five colours\", \"from\": 2856, \"to\": 2872}, {\"ngram\": \"the Olympic rings\", \"from\": 2876, \"to\": 2893}]}, {\"sentence\": \"But the message of a shared love of sport and unifying under one banner remains to this day.\", \"from\": 2920, \"to\": 3012, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the message\", \"from\": 2924, \"to\": 2935}, {\"ngram\": \"a shared love\", \"from\": 2939, \"to\": 2952}, {\"ngram\": \"sport\", \"from\": 2956, \"to\": 2961}, {\"ngram\": \"unifying\", \"from\": 2966, \"to\": 2974}, {\"ngram\": \"one banner\", \"from\": 2981, \"to\": 2991}, {\"ngram\": \"this day\", \"from\": 3003, \"to\": 3011}]}, {\"sentence\": \"SEARCH CONNECT WITH US TODAY'S PAPER See t